# Agent Workflow Rule

- Continue requested work end-to-end without stopping at partial progress.
- After meaningful edits, run build verification before considering work complete.
- If any runtime/build error appears, pause feature work and resolve the error first.
- After successful verification, provide recommended commit message(s).
